<span id="freeTextContainer15745019617732876381"><b>(C+) 65%</b> | Almost Satisfactory<br/><i>Notes:</i> A Sherlock Holmes story without the mystery. Suffers from the typical Chabon fluff, but without a redeemable story.</span>

