		    <b>
          <a title="Play Book Tag" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/22082442-the-final-solution---chabon---4-stars">Play Book Tag:</a>
        </b>
      
			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/22082442-the-final-solution---chabon---4-stars">The Final Solution - Chabon - 4 stars</a>
		</td>
		<td class="nobreak">
